Problem Statement: Develop a multi-page website for a college integrating various HTML concepts and navigation mechanisms.

Project Structure

CollegeWebsite/
│
├── index.html
├── departments.html
├── courses.html
├── contact.html
└── college.jpg

<!.. Home Page (index.html)  ..>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>ABC College - Home</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>ABC College</h1>

    <nav>
        <a href="index.html">Home</a> |
        <a href="departments.html">Departments</a> |
        <a href="courses.html">Courses</a> |
        <a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <hr>

    <img src="college.jpg" alt="College Campus" width="500">

    <h2>Welcome to ABC College</h2>

    <p>
        ABC College is committed to providing quality education
        and excellent career opportunities for students.
    </p>

</body>
</html>
